headline: EB5 Capital Celebrates the Closing of Atlanta Woodrow Apartments (JF41)
summary: WASHINGTON, July 24, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- EB5 Capital is pleased to announce the closing of its $42.4 million investment in Woodfield Development’s Atlanta Woodrow Apartments (JF41) project.
